{{version027}}

{{flavour|Speaks a word of chaos, forcing enemies nearby to blink away from the user. Additionally, those affected may be slowed, ensnared, or terrified by the experience. Invoking a word of chaos is no easy feat and will drain the user somewhat. Additionally, there will be a short time before the ability can be used again.}}


'''Word of Chaos''' is an [[ability]] acquired at rank 3 of the [[Corrupting Presence]] [[demonspawn mutation]]. This ability blinks away all enemies in [[LOS]]. Each enemy affected may additionally be [[ensnare]]d, [[slow]]ed, and/or [[Cause_Fear|frightened]].

{{crawlquote|'''Cost''': 6 MP, moderate [[drain]]ing, 15-24 turn cooldown<br>
'''Spell Power''': 40 + 6 Ã— [[XL]]<br>
'''Chance to Ensnare''': Spell Power / 500<br>
'''Chance to Slow''': Spell Power / 500<br>
'''Chance to Cause Fear''': Spell Power / 500
}}


==History==
*This ability was added in [[0.27]].

